tp.pr1.utils

Class Coords

  • java.lang.Object
    • tp.pr1.utils.Coords

  • public class Coords
extends java.lang.Object

    Coords class

    Represents a coordinate object

    Each coordinate has a row and a column

    Coordinates can be considered null coordinates (invalid, incorrect, or empty)
